contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox road |province=QC |type=QC |route=393 |maint=Transports Québec |map= |established= |decommissioned= |alternate_name= |length_km=98 |length_round=1 |length_ref=<ref>Ministère des transports, "Distances routières", page 95, Les Publications du Québec, 2005</ref> |direction_b=North |direction_a=South |terminus_a= {{jct|state=QC|QC|101}} in '''[[Rouyn-Noranda]]''' |terminus_b= ''[[Val-Paradis, Quebec|Val-Paradis]]'' in '''[[Baie-James, Quebec|Baie-James]]''' <br> (Route-des-Richesses) |previous_type=QC |previous_route=391 |next_type=QC |next_route=395 |cities= Rouyn-Noranda, La Sarre |junction= {{jct|state=QC|QC|111}} in La Sarre }} '''Route 393''' is a [[Quebec]] [[provincial highway]] located in the province's [[Abitibi-Témiscamingue]] and [[Nord-du-Québec]] regions. The highway runs from the junction of [[Quebec Route 101|Route 101]] in the Rouyn-Noranda suburb of Destor and ends in Val-Paradis in the municipality of Baie-James. In [[La Sarre]] it overlaps [[Quebec Route 111|Route 111]]. ==Municipalities along Route 393== * [[Rouyn-Noranda]] * [[Duparquet, Quebec|Duparquet]] * [[Rapide-Danseur, Quebec|Rapide-Danseur]] * [[Palmarolle, Quebec|Palmarolle]] * [[Sainte-Hélène-de-Mancebourg, Quebec|Sainte-Hélène-de-Mancebourg]] * [[La Sarre]] * [[Clermont, Abitibi-Témiscamingue, Quebec|Clermont]] (''[[Val-Saint-Gilles, Quebec|Val-Saint-Gilles]]'') * [[Baie-James, Quebec|Baie-James]] (''[[Beaucanton, Quebec|Beaucanton]]'' / ''[[Val-Paradis, Quebec|Val-Paradis]]'') ==See also== * [[List of Quebec provincial highways]] ==References== <references/> == External links == * [http://www.inforoutiere.qc.ca/fr/carte_routiere/index.asp Official Transports Quebec Map] {{fr icon}} * [http://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&saddr=RTE-393+%4048.502969,+-79.037016&daddr=RTE-393+%4048.905011,+-79.184603+to:49.153868,-79.289703&hl=en&geocode=1685491114599484275,48.502969,-79.037016%3B16847905059762874361,48.905011,-79.184603%3B7820406670618475468,49.159255,-79.243502&mra=dme&mrcr=0&mrsp=2&sz=13&via=1&dirflg=h&sll=49.153306,-79.282837&sspn=0.051646,0.154495&ie=UTF8&ll=48.862908,-79.291077&spn=0.831165,2.471924&z=9 Route 393] on Google Maps {{Secondary Highways in Quebec (300-series)}} [[Category:Quebec Routes|393]] [[Category:Transport in Rouyn-Noranda]] {{Quebec-road-stub}}
